---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Founder Scholarship — StartSuite"
  description="A scholarship program for founders at the protostar stage — earlier than pre-Series A. Same Brand HQ system, scoped engagement, partial scholarship."
>
  <section class="fs-hero">
    <div class="fs-hero-glow" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="fs-hero-orbits" aria-hidden="true">
      <span></span><span></span><span></span>
    </div>
    <div class="fs-hero-inner">
      <p class="fs-eyebrow">For protostars · Founder Scholarship</p>
      <h1>The earliest, dense, nascent moment.</h1>
      <p class="fs-hero-sub">An early-stage star is called a protostar. Gas and dust collapsing into a hot, dense core. The earliest stage of stellar formation, before what comes next.</p>
      <p class="fs-hero-sub fs-hero-sub-emph">If that's where you are, we have a path for you.</p>

      <div class="fs-card">
        <p class="fs-card-eyebrow">What it is</p>
        <p class="fs-card-body">The Founder Scholarship is a small cohort program for founders earlier than pre-Series A. You get the same Brand HQ system, a scoped engagement, and a partial scholarship covering a meaningful share of the build.</p>
        <ul class="fs-card-list">
          <li><strong>Cohort size</strong><span>Three founders per cohort, two cohorts a year.</span></li>
          <li><strong>Engagement</strong><span>Six weeks. Live Brand HQ ready to walk into.</span></li>
          <li><strong>Scholarship</strong><span>Partial coverage on engagement fees.</span></li>
          <li><strong>What we look for</strong><span>Real product. Real point of view. The protostar moment.</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="fs-hero-ctas">
        <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" onclick="openModal()" style="cursor:pointer">Apply to the program →</a>
        <a class="btn btn-outline btn-lg" href="/for-founders">See the full StartSuite for Founders →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="fs-back">
    <div class="fs-back-inner">
      <p class="fs-back-note">Have a peer who's protostar-stage? Send them this link.</p>
      <a class="fs-back-link" href="/">Back to StartSuite →</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .fs-hero{
    position:relative;
    padding:160px 48px 100px;
    overflow:hidden;
  }
  .fs-hero-glow{
    position:absolute;top:-180px;left:50%;
    transform:translateX(-50%);
    width:1100px;height:680px;
    background:radial-gradient(ellipse,rgba(139,109,181,0.16) 0%,transparent 65%);
    pointer-events:none;
  }
  .fs-hero-orbits{
    position:absolute;top:140px;left:50%;
    transform:translateX(-50%);
    width:520px;height:520px;
    pointer-events:none;
    z-index:0;
  }
  .fs-hero-orbits span{
    position:absolute;inset:0;border-radius:50%;
    border:1px dashed rgba(139,109,181,0.15);
  }
  .fs-hero-orbits span:nth-child(1){
    inset:25%;border-style:solid;border-color:rgba(139,109,181,0.18);
    animation:fsSpin 80s linear infinite;
  }
  .fs-hero-orbits span:nth-child(2){
    inset:12%;
    animation:fsSpin 130s linear infinite reverse;
  }
  .fs-hero-orbits span:nth-child(3){
    animation:fsSpin 200s linear infinite;
  }
  @keyframes fsSpin{
    from{transform:rotate(0deg)}
    to{transform:rotate(360deg)}
  }
  .fs-hero-inner{
    max-width:780px;margin:0 auto;
    position:relative;z-index:1;
    text-align:center;
    display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:24px;align-items:center;
  }
  .fs-eyebrow{
    font-family:var(--mono);
    font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.2em;
    text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--purple-light);
    margin:0;
  }
  .fs-hero h1{
    font-size:clamp(34px,5vw,64px);
    letter-spacing:-0.04em;line-height:1.05;
    color:var(--text);margin:0;font-weight:800;
    background:linear-gradient(160deg,#fff 30%,var(--accent) 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;
    background-clip:text;
  }
  .fs-hero-sub{
    font-size:16px;line-height:1.78;color:var(--text-muted);
    max-width:620px;margin:0;
  }
  .fs-hero-sub-emph{
    color:var(--text);font-weight:500;
  }
  .fs-card{
    width:100%;max-width:680px;
    margin-top:24px;
    padding:28px 32px;
    background:linear-gradient(160deg,rgba(139,109,181,0.06) 0%,rgba(139,109,181,0.015) 100%);
    border:1px solid rgba(139,109,181,0.18);
    border-radius:var(--radius-lg);
    text-align:left;
    display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:14px;
  }
  .fs-card-eyebrow{
    font-family:var(--mono);
    font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.18em;
    text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--purple-light);
    margin:0;
  }
  .fs-card-body{
    font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;color:var(--text);margin:0;
  }
  .fs-card-list{
    list-style:none;padding:0;margin:8px 0 0;
    display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:12px;
  }
  .fs-card-list li{
    display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:3px;
    padding:14px 16px;
    background:rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
    border:1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius:10px;
  }
  .fs-card-list strong{
    font-family:var(--mono);
    font-size:9px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.16em;
    text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--purple-light);
  }
  .fs-card-list span{
    font-size:13px;line-height:1.5;color:var(--text);
  }
  .fs-hero-ctas{
    display:flex;gap:14px;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center;margin-top:8px;
  }
  .fs-back{
    padding:60px 48px 100px;
    text-align:center;
    border-top:1px solid var(--border);
    margin-top:40px;
  }
  .fs-back-inner{
    max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;
    display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:14px;align-items:center;
  }
  .fs-back-note{
    font-size:13px;color:var(--text-muted);margin:0;
  }
  .fs-back-link{
    font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--purple-light);
    text-decoration:none;
    transition:color var(--duration) var(--ease);
  }
  .fs-back-link:hover{color:var(--text)}

  @media (max-width: 700px){
    .fs-hero{padding:120px 24px 80px}
    .fs-card{padding:22px 24px}
    .fs-card-list{grid-template-columns:1fr}
    .fs-hero-ctas{flex-direction:column;align-items:stretch;width:100%}
    .fs-hero-ctas .btn{justify-content:center}
    .fs-hero-orbits{width:380px;height:380px}
  }
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce){
    .fs-hero-orbits span{animation:none}
  }
</style>
